    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with positive Prick's test to at least one allergen and diagnosed as having
             allergic rhinitis were included

          -  Patients who used hypertonic nasal solution alone for at least one month were included
             as sthe study group

          -  Patients who used nasal steroid spray alone or at least one month were included as
             sthe study group

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with a history of asthma, urticeria, eczama, diabetes mellitus, hypertension,
             COPD and other systemic diseases were excluded
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
